    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
